
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I go to Page 07 of Thoracic CT

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Upper abdomen, kidney/adrenal gland' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Kidney' checkbox is enabled
And 'Mass adrenal gland' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Kidney' checkbox
Then 'Focal lesion' checkbox is enabled
And 'Urinary retention' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Focal lesion' checkbox
Then 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Classification' dropdown menu is enabled
And '> 1 lesion of the same entity' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Urinary retention' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Grade 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 3' radio button is enabled
And 'Grade 4' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Mass adrenal gland' checkbox
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Max. diameter' input field is enabled
And 'Classification' dropdown menu is enabled
